responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "6A7DAE2B4BB8860039A27E9B657853F2", "Warm sands and welcome to Verra. Though we do not share the gifts of Samia, you too can find refuge amongst the Vaelune. Let us share a journey of such enlightenment that begins with your first steps in Samia\'s Hope.")
